rComments: First of all do not depend on the final exam, its very overwhelming it requires a lot of writing. Lectures are fun and easy to keep up with, participation is important and it's easy mark. Sam is a good lecturer but in person it's hard to reach him and not very helpful. Group projects could be tricky and they mark everything so late. good luck.
Great prof. Group projects could get tricky though.

Overall very entertaining in lecture, but does expect a lot of student discussion. Lots of hidden material from discussion which ends up on the exam, and almost entirely group projects, which instructions are pretty unclear for.
Great prof! Material in lectures is very relevant and invites great guest speakers .

This guy walks around the lecture hall and just picks on students and expects them to know the answer to all his questions and when you don't know the answer he stands there frustrated and says "c'mon guys". Not even finished his masters yet. The exam was an insane amount of writing. Didn't get feedback on assignments until a month later.
